title: MobileAP

creator: Aboitiz Power Corporation
descriptionHtml:
MobileAP is your one-stop utility app for your accounts with Visayan Electric (VECO), Davao Light (DLPC), Cotabato Light (CLPC), Subic Enerzone, and LIMA Enerzone.

Stay in touch with your electricity bills anytime, anywhere!

- Register multiple accounts across 5 distribution utilities (DUs)
- Get confirmed as an account owner and manage your tenants
- Check your current and historical bill data and download them as e-bills (PDF)
- Track your payments and view charts for consumption and spending
- Pay your balances online with Unionbank, BPI, and RCBC
- Receive real-time notifications on new and updated bills, payments acknowledged, warning and advisory messages
- Find our service center locations and review all payment options
descriptionShort: Manage your VECO, Davao Light, Cotabato Light, Subic EZ and Lima EZ accounts.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Improved notifications and in-app messages with rich media
- UX/UI improvements
- Several vulnerability and bug fixes

- Monitor power interruptions that might affect your properties
